snippet.title: Super Pickleball Adventure Trailer
snippet.description:
https://bit.ly/PickleballGame

Super Pickleball Adventure is a free browser-based pickleball action adventure game! Challenge opponents that use a variety of techniques from ninjitsu to teleportation. Explore the world and meet a cast of wacky characters.
